&lt;b&gt; How FlexCloud work?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Just charge your 3€ credit during the order process and you will get 13€ avaiable funds that you can use to create your vms. Deploy a vm is easy and take just one minutes. Anytime you can change package upgrading and downgrading resource. 

&lt;b&gt;Fast FAQ&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
-) How am I billed?  &lt;br&gt;
Each FlexCloud is billed per hour up to its monthly cap. You can choose to fund your account via PayPal or you can pay your monthly bill via paypal or bank transfer.

-) When do you charge my account?&lt;br&gt;
We charge your credit card on the 1st day of each month after usage. You can pay invoice directly or keep fuds to auto-pay

-) How do I choose between monthly and hourly billing?&lt;br&gt;
Each VM is billed per hour up to its monthly cap. The monthly cost of your VM is calculated by running the hourly rate for 28 days (672 hours). When you choose a package you can see hourly price and monthly price. If you change package during the month we calculate the sum of days you used new and previous package.


